---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Rehabilitation Programming - Kalthoff Performance">
  <section class="min-h-screen bg-black text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-black mb-8 tracking-tight">Rehabilitation Programming</h1>
      
      <div class="relative w-full h-[400px] mb-12 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571902943202-507ec2618e8f?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" 
          alt="Physical therapy and rehabilitation session" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Rehabilitation is a critical component of both athletic performance and everyday life. My philosophy combines structured recovery protocols with performance training to ensure a safe, effective, and individualized approach to healing. Having collaborated extensively with physiotherapists and sports medicine professionals, I develop personalized rehab programs that address the root cause of injuries while rebuilding strength, mobility, and movement efficiency. Whether recovering from surgery, managing chronic pain, or overcoming an overuse injury, my goal is to restore individuals—athletes and non-athletes alike—to full function, pain-free movement, and a higher quality of life.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">What's Included</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Personalized rehabilitation protocols based on injury type and severity</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Progressive loading strategies for safe recovery</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Movement assessment and correction protocols</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Regular progress monitoring and program adjustments</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Program Delivery</h2>
        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Powered by TeamBuildr</h3>
          <img src="/images/full-logo-white-orange.png" alt="TeamBuildr Logo" class="h-12 mb-6" />
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            All programming is delivered through TeamBuildr, a professional training app that provides:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300 mt-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Easy-to-follow workout instructions with video demonstrations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Progress tracking and performance metrics</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Direct communication with your coach</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Who Is This For?</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Athletes recovering from injuries</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Individuals managing chronic pain or movement limitations</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Anyone looking to improve movement quality and prevent injuries</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-12 bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-8 border border-white/10">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Start Your Recovery Journey?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">
            Take the first step towards pain-free movement and improved quality of life with our expert rehabilitation programming.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="/pricing" class="inline-block bg-white text-black px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg font-bold tracking-wide hover:bg-gray-200 transition duration-300">
              View Pricing
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white/10 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg font-bold tracking-wide hover:bg-white/20 transition duration-300">
              Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout> 